{% extends "email/base.twig" %}
{% block content %}
    <p>Hi {{ name }},</p>
    <p>Great news! Traveling with your group just got even more fun and affordable—your group is now an official member of the Hi Flanders community. Welcome!</p>
    <p><strong>Your free membership includes:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>As a Hi Flanders member, your group will enjoy <a style="color: #fac000;" href="https://www.hiflanders.be/en/premium"><strong>exclusive benefits, discounts </strong></a> and  <a style="color: #fac000;" href="https://www.hiflanders.be/en/experiences"><strong>inspiration</strong></a> for future stays.</li>
        <li>And not just in Flanders—you’ll also save on hostel stays worldwide! Your group now has automatic access to the world’s largest hostel network: <strong>Hostelling International</strong> (HI). That means peaceful nights worldwide at the best rates. <a style="color: #fac000;" href="https://www.hiflanders.be/en/hostelling-international">Find inspiration for an international trip or city getaway here.</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p>Prefer to stay closer to home? <a style="color: #fac000;" href="https://www.hiflanders.be/en/destinations">Book your stay at one of our hostels in Flanders.</a> Looking for fun activities nearby? Thanks to our <a style="color: #fac000;" href="https://www.hiflanders.be/en/experiences">Experiences page,</a> your group will never run out of things to do!</p>
    <p>We hope to welcome you and your group to one of our hostels soon!</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 30px">Warm regards,</p>
    <p><strong>The Hi Flanders Team</strong></p>
{% endblock %}
